{"tid":1881701,"cid":28,"subCid":0,"title":"(大家幫手推)揾晒所有人啦，唔該連仔幫手del po~","createTime":"2020-02-15T17:22:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-16T05:56:07.000Z","uid":142002,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a1bdf073e4a7190d9f81cd6e27595e65b3adbc07","tid":1881701,"uid":142002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T17:22:45.000Z","msg":"唔該晒連仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n辛苦晒各位手足，好多謝大家唔放棄被捕手足<br />\n我正式宣布天水圍手足唔係condom<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望大家繼續follow up將來佢地上庭去聲援<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nPS.連仔如果可以順手幫我del埋呢個po<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fd850727a79923cee542ec285b1d8c04a3ab8d3","tid":1881701,"uid":142002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T17:22:54.000Z","msg":"推一"},{"pid":"4193ab0146923c266bc91b9bad17410354e95ee3","tid":1881701,"uid":142002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T17:23:10.000Z","msg":"自推二"},{"pid":"dda2aa25f15006a35f9f318d2f6d6bf03e3e3705","tid":1881701,"uid":142002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T17:25:06.000Z","msg":"推三"},{"pid":"d7043ad1d54612401a09f97fc07008cc89b36dcf","tid":1881701,"uid":142002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T17:25:17.000Z","msg":"推四"},{"pid":"69bc9feb34738a4b2657a171e3f7d9899e690807","tid":1881701,"uid":142002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T17:25:30.000Z","msg":"五推"},{"pid":"64a3b6eee97563124ab66d5becfac87ce8c8dd29","tid":1881701,"uid":142002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T17:25:41.000Z","msg":"6推"},{"pid":"174a7912ba3ddaee1f2225d90bec088eb4111f70","tid":1881701,"uid":142002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"reply